{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'Actually standing on a stage like this feels so different from seeing them in a projection.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Liv closes her eyes, seemingly allowing herself to fully experience the moment.'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'What a rare experience...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Sorry for being brusque about it, but why did you want to invite me here, Commandant?', 4: '1'}
{2: "I thought you'd like it here.", 3: '11', 4: 'Do you like it here, Liv?', 5: '12'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'I do like this place a lot. I feel like even the air here smells different.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'The maze is not the only thing I like.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'I like it here because of the place itself but also because of you, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "This place only feels so different because I'm standing with you.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Liv takes a deep breath and turns toward you.'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "I don't know if we can be like that... but I'm glad.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "I'm glad you chose me to explore such a special place together, Commandant. I'm glad we get to experience everything we've been through.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "I'm glad to know you, Commandant.", 4: '1'}
{2: "I'm glad to know you too, Liv."}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "We'll be together forever, won't we, Commandant?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Nothing will separate us, whether it is war or something else, right?', 4: '1'}
{2: "We'll be together forever.", 3: '27'}
{3: 'The girl with white hair seems to have dropped a tear, but it quickly disappears.'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Can we stay here for a little longer, Commandant?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Will you look around with me?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Liv looks shy, having made a request for once.'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Thanks, Commandant. I was hoping to check out the beach there first...', 4: '1'}
